#. <section class="sutta" id="sn55.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Veḷudvāravagga"
msgstr "1. At Bamboo Gate"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Paṭhamagiñjakāvasathasutta"
msgstr "8. In the Brick Hall (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.8:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "sn55.8:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā ñātike viharati giñjakāvasathe."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying at Nādika in the brick house."

msgctxt "sn55.8:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.8:2.1"
msgid "“Sāḷho nāma, bhante, bhikkhu kālaṅkato;"
msgstr "“Sir, the monk named Sāḷha has passed away."

msgctxt "sn55.8:2.2"
msgid "tassa kā gati ko abhisamparāyo?"
msgstr "Where has he been reborn in his next life?"

msgctxt "sn55.8:2.3"
msgid "Nandā nāma, bhante, bhikkhunī kālaṅkatā;"
msgstr "The nun named Nandā,"

msgctxt "sn55.8:2.4"
msgid "tassā kā gati ko abhisamparāyo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.8:2.5"
msgid "Sudatto nāma, bhante, upāsako kālaṅkato;"
msgstr "the layman named Sudatta,"

msgctxt "sn55.8:2.6"
msgid "tassa kā gati ko abhisamparāyo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.8:2.7"
msgid "Sujātā nāma, bhante, upāsikā kālaṅkatā;"
msgstr "and the laywoman named Sujātā have passed away."

msgctxt "sn55.8:2.8"
msgid "tassā kā gati, ko abhisamparāyo”ti?"
msgstr "Where have they been reborn in the next life?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.357"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.8:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Sāḷho, ānanda, bhikkhu kālaṅkato āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ "
"paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihāsi."
msgstr ""
"“Ānanda, the monk Sāḷha passed away having realized the undefiled freedom of "
"heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life, having realized it with his "
"own insight due to the ending of defilements."

msgctxt "sn55.8:3.2"
msgid ""
"Nandā, ānanda, bhikkhunī kālaṅkatā pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ "
"parikkhayā opapātikā tattha parinibbāyinī anāvattidhammā tasmā lokā."
msgstr ""
"The nun Nandā passed away having ended the five lower fetters. She’s been "
"reborn spontaneously, and will be extinguished there, not liable to return "
"from that world."

msgctxt "sn55.8:3.3"
msgid ""
"Sudatto, ānanda, upāsako kālaṅkato tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā "
"rāgadosamohānaṃ tanuttā sakadāgāmī; sakideva imaṃ lokaṃ āgantvā "
"dukkhassantaṃ karissati."
msgstr ""
"The layman Sudatta passed away having ended three fetters, and weakened "
"greed, hate, and delusion. He’s a once-returner; he will come back to this "
"world once only, then make an end of suffering."

msgctxt "sn55.8:3.4"
msgid ""
"Sujātā, ānanda, upāsikā kālaṅkatā tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā sotāpannā "
"avinipātadhammā niyatā sambodhiparāyaṇā."
msgstr ""
"The laywoman Sujātā passed away having ended three fetters. She’s a stream-"
"enterer, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.8:4.1"
msgid "Anacchariyaṃ kho panetaṃ, ānanda, yaṃ manussabhūto kālaṃ kareyya;"
msgstr "It’s hardly surprising that a human being should pass away."

msgctxt "sn55.8:4.2"
msgid ""
"tasmiṃ tasmiñce maṃ kālaṅkate upasaṅkamitvā etamatthaṃ paṭipucchissatha. "
"Vihesā pesā, ānanda, assa tathāgatassa."
msgstr ""
"But if you should come and ask me about it each and every time someone dies "
"that would be a bother for me."

msgctxt "sn55.8:4.3"
msgid ""
"Tasmātihānanda, dhammādāsaṃ nāma dhammapariyāyaṃ desessāmi; yena samannāgato "
"ariyasāvako ākaṅkhamāno attanāva attānaṃ byākareyya:"
msgstr ""
"So Ānanda, I will teach you the explanation of the Dhamma called ‘the mirror "
"of the teaching’. A noble disciple who has this may declare of themselves:"

msgctxt "sn55.8:4.4"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo "
"khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto, sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato "
"sambodhiparāyaṇo’."
msgstr ""
"‘I’ve finished with rebirth in hell, the animal realm, and the ghost realm. "
"I’ve finished with all places of loss, bad places, the underworld. I am a "
"stream-enterer! I’m not liable to be reborn in the underworld, and am bound "
"for awakening.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.8:5.1"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca so, ānanda, dhammādāso dhammapariyāyo; yena samannāgato "
"ariyasāvako ākaṅkhamāno attanāva attānaṃ byākareyya:"
msgstr "And what is that mirror of the teaching?"

msgctxt "sn55.8:5.2"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo "
"khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto, sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato "
"sambodhiparāyaṇo’?"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.8:6.1"
msgid ""
"Idha, ānanda, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—itipi so "
"bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti."
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn55.8:6.2"
msgid "Dhamme … pe …"
msgstr "the teaching …"

msgctxt "sn55.8:6.3"
msgid "saṅghe … pe …"
msgstr "the Saṅgha …"

msgctxt "sn55.8:6.4"
msgid ""
"ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi."
msgstr ""
"And they have the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to "
"immersion."

msgctxt "sn55.8:6.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho so, ānanda, dhammādāso dhammapariyāyo;"
msgstr "This is that mirror of the teaching."

msgctxt "sn55.8:6.6"
msgid "yena samannāgato ariyasāvako ākaṅkhamāno attanāva attānaṃ byākareyya:"
msgstr "A noble disciple who has this may declare of themselves:"

msgctxt "sn55.8:6.7"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo "
"khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto, sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato "
"sambodhiparāyaṇo’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I’ve finished with rebirth in hell, the animal realm, and the ghost realm. "
"I’ve finished with all places of loss, bad places, the underworld. I am a "
"stream-enterer! I’m not liable to be reborn in the underworld, and am bound "
"for awakening.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.8:6.8"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.8:6.9"
msgid "(Tīṇipi suttantāni ekanidānāni.)"
msgstr "(The following two discourses have the same setting.)"
